portpkg: Portpkg (Administration tools for the Portpkg Project)
portpkg:
portpkg: These are the administration tools portpkg, autoport,
portpkg: checkpkg, pp-clean-cache, pp-sync-dist, pp-sync-slack and
portpkg: pp-export. For more docmentation see /usr/doc/portpkg-xxx or
portpkg: http://portpkg.berlios.de. Checkout the ports tree with
portpkg: 'portpkg --sync'.
portpkg: PLEASE NOTE: If you have Slackware-current, do
portpkg:   # echo pasture/ >>/usr/ports/exclude.local
portpkg: AND ALSO: If you want to use mirrors make a symlink
portpkg:   # ln -s mirrors.de /usr/ports/mirrors
